Nexo DevOps Task

The goal is to set up CI/CD process for backend application.

Minimum requirements:
1. Hello world application written on any language running inside Docker
2. Local environment with docker compose
3. Automated docker build &amp; push process with any CI tools like Github Actions,
TravisCI, etc.
4. Deploy to local Kubernetes environment like minikube.

Optional:
1. Connect the application to SQL database running inside the cluster.
2. Deploy the application using helm.
Everything should be in the git repository with commits
